lv.lumii.layoutengine.flowLayout.horizontalOrdering

Class OrderingAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • lv.lumii.layoutengine.flowLayout.horizontalOrdering.OrderingAlgorithm

  • public class OrderingAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the main control structures of the horizontal ordering algorithm of a layered graph that is needed to provide the horizontal ordering in the Flow Layout algorithm. The algorithm runs in two stages: (1) building node PQ-trees processing levels in top to bottom order, (2) determining node ordering within levels in level bottom to top order according PQ-tree data.
